1 SECTION 2. APPROPRIATION - DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC INSTRUCTION - SCHOOL
2 BUILDING ASSESSMENTS - ONE-TIME FUNDING. There is appropriated out of any moneys
3 in the general fund in the state treasury, not otherwise appropriated, the sum of $4,000,000, or
4 so much of the sum as may be necessary, to the department of public instruction for the
5 purpose of providing for a statewide facilities assessment for the biennium beginning July 1,
6 2025, and ending June 30, 2027. The funding provided in this section is considered a one-time
7 funding item.
